            "content_html": "<blockquote>\n<p>128/3/1</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar__GM2\" id=\"i-к°ңмҡ”\">I. к°ңмҡ”<a href=\"https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/sw/cohesion-vs-coupling#i-%EA%B0%9C%EC%9A%94\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to heading\" title=\"Direct link to heading\">вҖӢ</a></h2>\n<h3 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar__GM2\" id=\"к°ңл…җ\">к°ңл…җ<a href=\"https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/sw/cohesion-vs-coupling#%EA%B0%9C%EB%85%90\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to heading\" title=\"Direct link to heading\">вҖӢ</a></h3>\n<p>к°ңл…җлҸ„ лҳҗлҠ” кҙҖкі„лҸ„</p>\n<h3 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar__GM2\" id=\"л°°кІҪ\">л°°кІҪ<a href=\"https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/sw/cohesion-vs-coupling#%EB%B0%B0%EA%B2%BD\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to heading\" title=\"Direct link to heading\">вҖӢ</a></h3>\n<p>мөңк·ј MSA м Ғмҡ©м—җ л”°лҘё лӘЁл“Ҳнҷ”мқҳ мӨ‘мҡ”м„ұмқҙ мҰқк°Җлҗҳм—Ҳкі , MSAмқҳ к°Ғ м„ңл№„мҠӨ лӢЁмң„лҠ” мқ‘м§‘лҸ„к°Җ лҶ’кі  кІ°н•©лҸ„к°Җ лӮ®кІҢ кө¬нҳ„лҗҳм–ҙм•јн•Ё.</p>\n<h2 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar__GM2\" id=\"ii-кө¬мЎ°-н•өмӢ¬мҡ”мҶҢ-м Ғмҡ©л°©м•Ҳ\">II. кө¬мЎ°, н•өмӢ¬мҡ”мҶҢ, м Ғмҡ©л°©м•Ҳ<a href=\"https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/sw/cohesion-vs-coupling#ii-%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0-%ED%95%B5%EC%8B%AC%EC%9A%94%EC%86%8C-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%EB%B0%A9%EC%95%88\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to heading\" title=\"Direct link to heading\">вҖӢ</a></h2>\n<h3 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar__GM2\" id=\"к°Җ-кө¬мЎ°-кө¬м„ұлҸ„-к°ңл…җлҸ„\">к°Җ. кө¬мЎ° (кө¬м„ұлҸ„, к°ңл…җлҸ„)<a href=\"https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/sw/cohesion-vs-coupling#%EA%B0%80-%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1%EB%8F%84-%EA%B0%9C%EB%85%90%EB%8F%84\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to heading\" title=\"Direct link to heading\">вҖӢ</a></h3>\n<h3 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar__GM2\" id=\"лӮҳ-н•өмӢ¬мҡ”мҶҢ\">лӮҳ. н•өмӢ¬мҡ”мҶҢ<a href=\"https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/sw/cohesion-vs-coupli