            "content_html": "<blockquote>\n<p>130/4/6</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar__GM2\" id=\"i-к°ңмҡ”\">I. к°ңмҡ”<a href=\"https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/sw/dataops-vs-devops#i-%EA%B0%9C%EC%9A%94\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to heading\" title=\"Direct link to heading\">вҖӢ</a></h2>\n<h3 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar__GM2\" id=\"к°Җ-лҚ°мқҙн„°мҳөмҠӨ-лҚ°лёҢмҳөмҠӨ-к°ңл…җ\">к°Җ. лҚ°мқҙн„°мҳөмҠӨ, лҚ°лёҢмҳөмҠӨ к°ңл…җ<a href=\"https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/sw/dataops-vs-devops#%EA%B0%80-%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%84%B0%EC%98%B5%EC%8A%A4-%EB%8D%B0%EB%B8%8C%EC%98%B5%EC%8A%A4-%EA%B0%9C%EB%85%90\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to heading\" title=\"Direct link to heading\">вҖӢ</a></h3>\n<!-- -->\n<h3 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar__GM2\" id=\"лӮҳ-л°°кІҪ\">лӮҳ. л°°кІҪ<a href=\"https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/sw/dataops-vs-devops#%EB%82%98-%EB%B0%B0%EA%B2%BD\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to heading\" title=\"Direct link to heading\">вҖӢ</a></h3>\n<!-- -->\n<p>л””м§Җн„ёнҠёлһңмҠӨнҸ¬л©”мқҙм…ҳмңјлЎң мқён•ң л№…лҚ°мқҙн„°, DevOpsмқҳ мӨ‘мҡ”м„ұ мҰқк°Җ.</p>\n<h2 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar__GM2\" id=\"ii-лҚ°мқҙн„°мҳөмҠӨ-м•„нӮӨн…ҚмІҳ\">II. лҚ°мқҙн„°мҳөмҠӨ м•„нӮӨн…ҚмІҳ<a href=\"https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/sw/dataops-vs-devops#ii-%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%84%B0%EC%98%B5%EC%8A%A4-%EC%95%84%ED%82%A4%ED%85%8D%EC%B2%98\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to heading\" title=\"Direct link to heading\">вҖӢ</a></h2>\n<p>к°Җ. ~мқҳ кө¬мЎ° (кө¬м„ұлҸ„, к°ңл…җлҸ„)\nлӮҳ. ~мқҳ н•өмӢ¬мҡ”мҶҢ\nк°Җ.м—җ к·ёлҰ° лӢӨмқҙм–ҙк·ёлһЁмқ„ 3лӢЁ н‘ңлЎң мһ‘м„ұ</p>\n<table><thead><tr><th>кө¬л¶„</th><th>лӮҙмҡ©</th><th>л№„кі </th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>-</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar__GM2\" id=\"iii-лҚ°мқҙн„°мҳөмҠӨ-пҝҪпҝҪмЈјмҡ”-кё°мҲ \">III. лҚ°мқҙн„°мҳөмҠӨ мЈјмҡ” кё°мҲ <a href=\"https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/sw/dataops-vs-devops#iii-%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%84%B0%EC%98%B5%EC%8A%A4-%EC%A3%BC%EC%9A%94-%EA%B8%B0%EC%88%A0\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to heading\" title=\"Direct link to heading\">вҖӢ</a></h2>\n<p>к°Җ. ~мқҳ м Ғмҡ© м „лһө\nSWOT л¶„м„қ</p>\n<p>лӮҳ. ~мқҳ м Ғмҡ© л°©м•Ҳ</p>\n<table><thead><tr><th>кө¬л¶„</th><th>лӮҙмҡ©</th><th>л№„кі </th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>кіөкіө</td><td>(лҢҖкөӯлҜјм„ңл№„мҠӨ н–ҘмғҒ)</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>кёҲмңө</td><td>(к°Җмҡ©м„ұ)</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>лҜјк°„</td><td>(мқҙмңӨм¶”кө¬)</td><td>-</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>м–ҙл Өмҡё кІҪмҡ°</p>\n<table><thead><tr><th>кө¬л¶„</th><th>лӮҙмҡ©</th><th>л№„кі </th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>л№„м§ҖлӢҲмҠӨ кҙҖм җ</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>кё°мҲ  кҙҖм җ</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>ліҙм•Ҳ кҙҖм җ</td><td>-</td><td>-</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar__GM2\" id=\"iv-лҚ°мқҙн„°мҳөмҠӨмқҳ-м¶”к°Җм Ғмқё-кі л ӨмӮ¬н•ӯ\">IV. лҚ°мқҙн„°мҳөмҠӨмқҳ м¶”к°Җм Ғмқё кі л ӨмӮ¬н•ӯ<a href=\"https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/sw/dataops-vs-devops#iv-%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%84%B0%EC%98%B5%EC%8A%A4%EC%9D%98-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80%EC%A0%81%EC%9D%B8-%EA%B3%A0%EB%A0%A4%EC%82%AC%ED%95%AD\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to heading\" title=\"Direct link to heading\">вҖӢ</a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>AIлҘј нҷңмҡ©н•ҳлҠ” MLOpsлЎңк№Ңм§Җ нҷ•мһҘн•ҳм—¬, лҚ°мқҙн„° кё°л°ҳмқҳ мқҳмӮ¬кІ°м •мқ„ лҚ” л№ лҘҙкІҢ к°Җм ёк°Ҳ мҲҳ мһҲмқҢ.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\"лҒқ\"</p>",
