            "content_html": "<blockquote>\n<p>131/3/4</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar__GM2\" id=\"i-к°ңмҡ”\">I. к°ңмҡ”<a href=\"https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/sw/safety-analysis#i-%EA%B0%9C%EC%9A%94\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to heading\" title=\"Direct link to heading\">вҖӢ</a></h2>\n<p>IoT, IoE мӢңлҢҖк°Җ лҸ„лһҳн•Ём—җ л”°лқј, лӘЁл“  IT л””л°”мқҙмҠӨк°Җ мӮ¬лһҢм—җкІҢ мң„н—ҳмҡ”мқёмқҙ лҗ  мҲҳ мһҲмқҢ. мң„н—ҳмқ„ нҡҢн”ј, м „к°Җ, к°җмҶҢ, мҲҳмҡ©, мқҙкҙҖн•ҳкё° мң„н•ҙ SW м•Ҳм •м„ұ л¶„м„қ н•„мҡ”.</p>\n<h2 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar__GM2\" id=\"ii-fta-л¶„м„қ-кё°лІ•кіј-м Ҳм°Ё\">II. FTA л¶„м„қ кё°лІ•кіј м Ҳм°Ё<a href=\"https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/sw/safety-analysis#ii-fta-%EB%B6%84%EC%84%9D-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B2%95%EA%B3%BC-%EC%A0%88%EC%B0%A8\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to heading\" title=\"Direct link to heading\">вҖӢ</a></h2>\n<h2 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar__GM2\" id=\"iii-fmea-л¶„м„қ-кё°лІ•кіј-м Ҳм°Ё\">III. FMEA л¶„м„қ кё°лІ•кіј м Ҳм°Ё<a href=\"https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/sw/safety-analysis#iii-fmea-%EB%B6%84%EC%84%9D-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B2%95%EA%B3%BC-%EC%A0%88%EC%B0%A8\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to heading\" title=\"Direct link to heading\">вҖӢ</a></h2>\n<h2 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar__GM2\" id=\"iv-hazop-л¶„м„қ-кё°лІ•кіј-м Ҳм°Ё\">IV. HAZOP л¶„м„қ кё°лІ•кіј м Ҳм°Ё<a href=\"https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/sw/safety-analysis#iv-hazop-%EB%B6%84%EC%84%9D-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B2%95%EA%B3%BC-%EC%A0%88%EC%B0%A8\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to heading\" title=\"Direct link to heading\">вҖӢ</a></h2>\n<p>\"лҒқ\"</p>",
