            "content_html": "<blockquote>\n<p>129/2/6</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar__GM2\" id=\"i-к°ңмҡ”\">I. к°ңмҡ”<a href=\"https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/sw/refactoring#i-%EA%B0%9C%EC%9A%94\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to heading\" title=\"Direct link to heading\">вҖӢ</a></h2>\n<h3 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar__GM2\" id=\"к°ңл…җ\">к°ңл…җ<a href=\"https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/sw/refactoring#%EA%B0%9C%EB%85%90\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to heading\" title=\"Direct link to heading\">вҖӢ</a></h3>\n<!-- -->\n<p>мҷёл¶Җм Ғ кё°лҠҘмқҖ мҲҳм •н•ҳм§Җ м•Ҡкі , лӮҙл¶ҖлҘј лӢЁмҲңнҷ”н•ҳм—¬ мң м§ҖліҙмҲҳм„ұмқ„ н–ҘмғҒмӢңнӮӨлҠ” кё°лІ•</p>\n<h3 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar__GM2\" id=\"л°°кІҪ\">л°°кІҪ<a href=\"https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/sw/refactoring#%EB%B0%B0%EA%B2%BD\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to heading\" title=\"Direct link to heading\">вҖӢ</a></h3>\n<p>м• мһҗмқј к°ңл°ң л°©лІ•лЎ мқҳ лҸ„мһ…мңјлЎң TDDлҘј кё°л°ҳмңјлЎң мҪ”л“ңмҠӨл©ңмқ„ м ңкұ°н•ҳкё° мң„н•ң лҰ¬нҢ©нҶ л§Ғмқҳ мӨ‘мҡ”м„ұмқҙ к°•мЎ°лҗЁ.</p>\n<h2 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar__GM2\" id=\"ii-лҰ¬нҢ©нҶ л§Ғмқҳ-н•өмӢ¬мҡ”мҶҢ-м Ғмҡ©л°©м•Ҳ\">II. лҰ¬нҢ©нҶ л§Ғмқҳ н•өмӢ¬мҡ”мҶҢ, м Ғмҡ©л°©м•Ҳ<a href=\"https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/sw/refactoring#ii-%EB%A6%AC%ED%8C%A9%ED%86%A0%EB%A7%81%EC%9D%98-%ED%95%B5%EC%8B%AC%EC%9A%94%EC%86%8C-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%EB%B0%A9%EC%95%88\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to heading\" title=\"Direct link to heading\">вҖӢ</a></h2>\n<h3 class=\"anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar__GM2\" id=\"к°Җ-лҰ¬нҢ©нҶ л§Ғмқҳ-кө¬мЎ°-кө¬м„ұлҸ„-к°ңл…җлҸ„\">к°Җ. лҰ¬нҢ©нҶ л§Ғмқҳ кө¬мЎ° (кө¬м„ұлҸ„, к°ңл…җлҸ„)<a href=\"https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/sw/refactoring#%EA%B0%80-%EB%A6%AC%ED%8C%A9%ED%86%A0%EB%A7%81%EC%9D%98-%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1%EB%8F%84-%EA%B0%9C%EB%85%90%EB%8F%84\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to heading\" title=\"Direct link to heading\">вҖӢ</a></h3>\n<h3 cla